Package GoNature

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AvailableOrders
    AvailableOrders represents information about available orders for booking at a specific park on a given date and time.
    CanceledReport
    CanceledReport represents a report containing information about canceled automatic, manual, and not-come orders, along with their corresponding percentages.
    ClientInfo
    ClientInfo represents information about a client, including host, IP address, and status.
    Employee
    Employee represents an employee working within the system.
    NonFullTimes
    NonFullTimes represents information about non-full time slots for a specific date and time range.
    NonFullTimesReport
    NonFullTimesReport represents a report containing information about non-full time slots and least full hours in a day.
    Options
    Options represents a set of options for communication between client and server.
    Order
    Order represents a reservation order made by a visitor to visit a park.
    Park
    Park represents a park in the system with details such as park name, current number of visitors, maximum capacity of visitors, and time limit for visitors.
    Report
    Report represents a report submitted by a user regarding a specific park.
    Request
    Request represents a request made by a user regarding a specific park.
    TotalVisitorsReport
    TotalVisitorsReport represents a report containing information about total visitors to a park.
    Traveler
    The Traveler class represents a traveler who may have booked visits to parks.
    UnplannedOrder  
    Visit
    The Visit class represents a visit to a park made by travelers.
    VisitorsTypeReport
    The VisitorsTypeReport class represents a report containing the number of visitors by type (individual, family, and group) per hour in the day ovre the last month.
  • Enum Summary

    Options.Option
    Enum representing different communication options.
    Order.OrderType
    Enum representing different types of orders.
    Request.RequestType
    Enum defining different types of requests.
